  <description>
    <p>
      Zerra System Cleaner is a lightweight and safe system cleaning utility designed for Linux.
      It helps users recover disk space by cleaning unnecessary files while keeping your system safe.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Clean APT cache and package archives</li>
      <li>Remove old system logs and journals</li>
      <li>Clear application caches (browser, thumbnails, etc.)</li>
      <li>Automatic maintenance scheduling</li>
      <li>Cleaning history tracking</li>
      <li>Native GTK interface</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
  
